urls.title: Hurricane Preparedness Information | City of Weston, FL
urls.description: Hurricane season is June 1 through November 30. Before the season begins, you should have a plan for your family, home and business that you can implement should a storm threaten our area. The City of Weston staff are trained in the National Incident Management System (NIMS) for emergency operation activations. Should a storm threaten our area, the City would activate its Emergency Operations Center and prepare for the possible impacts the storm would have due to high velocity winds, excessive rain, etc.
